changelog: Anti Spam in Better Chat can now detect multi-line messages
Added No Blind, No Darkness, Message Signature Indicator and No Glowing to No Render
Slightly improved consistency of the GUI
Removed No Signatures from Server Spoof, it was just much much worse version of the standalone mod
Added Armor Swap to Inventory Tweaks
Added Target FPS to Unfocused CPU
The .toggle command now sends chat feedback
Added Cancel Blink keybind to Blink
Added Auto Hover to Elytra Fly
Use laby.net API instead of Mojang's removed name history API
Added second mode to the .server plugins command
Added Drop Spawn Packets to No render
Split Always Show setting to multiple Hide Flags settings in Better Tooltips
Added friend color override setting to ESP and Tracers
And lastly A LOT of bug fixes
